programme.title: The Cave
programme.desc: Apabila pasukan bola sepak remaja yang terdiri daripada 12 lelaki, berumur 11-16, dan jurulatih mereka berusia 25 tahun terperangkap jauh di dalam gua di Utara Thailand, beribu-ribu sukarelawan dan tentera dari seluruh dunia bersatu dalam perlumbaan melawan masa untuk mencari mereka . Sebaik sahaja kanak-kanak lelaki itu ditemui hidup sepuluh hari kemudian, satu-satunya jalan keluar ialah berenang selama lima jam yang mustahil yang hanya penyelam gua yang pakar boleh bertahan. Di Ireland, juruelektrik kilang kapal terbang dan penyelam gua rekreasi Jim Warny menerima panggilan: "Berapa lama lagi anda boleh berada di sini?" Tiba di Thailand, Jim melangkah keluar dari pesawat dan masuk ke dalam guamisi tiga hari bermata pisau sedang dijalankan. Berdasarkan peristiwa sebenar, THE CAVE menceritakan kisah mendebarkan tentang misi menyelamat antarabangsa terbesar pada zaman moden, dari perspektif unik lelaki dan wanita yang menghadapi keputusan hidup dan mati dan mempamerkan keazaman dan pengorbanan yang tidak mementingkan diri sendiri, yang memuncak dengan keputusan yang berjaya menentang semua kemungkinan.

programme.title: Plan B Ep1
programme.desc: Episod pertama ini mengisahkan Khai dan Airis kedua-dua mereka daripada keluarga kaya mempertaruhkan wang dalam satu perlumbaan haram kereta "drift". Airis memenangi perlumbaan itu dengan imbuhan wang sebanyak RM20 ribu. Khai tidak berpuas hati, kerana Airis yang dikatakan baru dalam aktiviti ini dengan mudah mengalahkannya. Khai meneruskan usahanya untuk berkenalan dengan Airis dengan bantuan rakanya, Que mendapatkan butir peribadi, Airis menerusi laman sosial "FB".

programme.title: Kapsul
programme.desc: Kapsul masa wawasan 2020 yang ditanam oleh Tun Dr. Mahathir Mohamad telah dicuri dan membawa Zohri ( Faizal Hussein ) kembali ke masa lalu. Zohri kini terperangkap di tengah-tengah pergolakan bangsa Melayu untuk mencapai kemerdekaan dan membawa bangsa Melayu keluar dari belenggu kemiskinan. Zohri melihat dan merasai sendiri erti perjuangan umatnya yang tidak pernah dibayangkannya selama ini. Dia lihat, dia rasa dan kini dia mula faham betapa peritnya liku-liku sejarah negara dan bangsa. Perjalanan Zohri berterusan dari satu zaman ke satu zaman dan tiada siapa yang dapat mengembalikannya ke zamannya melainkan dirinya sendiri.

programme.title: UC 2
programme.desc: Sepasang suami isteri yang bahagia mula mengalami mimpi ngeri di rumah mereka apabila perbuatan ghaib dan misteri mula berlaku.

programme.title: Mantera Anjasmoro Ep5
programme.desc: Episod ini mengisahkan ibubapa Suria marah selepas mengetahui Suria berkahwin tanpa memohon restu. Ibubapa Zahid pula menasihatkan Zahid supaya jangan menceraikan Sabrina kerana cucu mereka akan dilahirkan. Kini Zahid jarang pulang ke rumah, bomoh Ramona mengingatkan Sabrina menggunakan minyak jampi dengan yakin setiap hari.

programme.title: Hantu Tenggek
programme.desc: Sekumpulan penipu yang diketuai oleh Tariq yang berpura-pura mengusir tempat berhantu telah diperas ugut oleh Tuan Sidek, seorang pemaju bangunan. Mereka perlu meyakinkan pesaing Tuan Sidek bahawa bangunan tertentu berhantu apabila mereka terperangkap di dalamnya. Kecuali mereka tidak perlu meyakinkan kerana bangunan itu benar-benar dihantui oleh roh yang tidak tenteram. Roh memerlukan bantuan mereka untuk memenuhi hasrat terakhirnya

programme.title: Plan B Ep2
programme.desc: Episod ke-2 mengisahkan Khai berjaya memujuk Airis menemankannya minum setelah membawanya bersiar-siar melihat suasana Kuala Lumpur dari udara dengan kapal terbang jenis ringan miliknya. Que pula seorang pelajar kolej salah seorang daripada rakan Khai sedang diintip dan diekori polis. Kemudian Airis bersetuju berlumba kereta secara haram dengan Khai, sebagai satu syarat untuk keluar bagi kali kedua bersama-sama minum dengannya. Setelah Khai memenangi perlumbaan kereta iru, Airis seterusnya mencabar Khai supaya melakukan aktiviti yang lebih mencabar, iaitu mencuri kereta, kononnya sematamata sebagai satu hiburan sahaja.

programme.title: Pipeline
programme.desc: Semasa pengusir setan Do-jin menuju ke pusat komuniti terbiar dengan khabar angin tentang kematian aneh, dia bertemu 3 pelajar kolej di sana untuk menangkap peristiwa yang dikhabarkan dan menyedari mereka terperangkap

programme.title: 3AM Ep1
programme.desc: Pesta Hantu Lapar sudah hampir. Seorang pekerja baru di telah menyinggung perasaan hantu di bangunan pejabatnya kerana dia tidak hormat kepada roh pada hari pertamanya bekerja. Semasa menjalani syif malam, lelaki itu dan rakan sekerjanya yang bekerja lebih masa mengalami pertemuan menyeramkan yang membuatkan mereka merenung tingkah laku dan kepercayaan mereka.

programme.title: Arjuna Ep1
programme.desc: Istana Adipura diserang oleh musuh mereka, Grakus dan pengikut-pengikutnya Lang Kajai dan Nading. Untungnya, Arjuna, anak Adipura dan Rupasari sempat dibawa lari dan dihanyutkan oleh ibu saudaranya, Cintasari. Arjuna membesar tanpa mengetahui kisah silamnya sehinggalah berlaku pergaduhan dan dia diselamatkan oleh Mikael dan Suria.

programme.title: Pipeline
programme.desc: Semasa pengusir setan Do-jin menuju ke pusat komuniti terbiar dengan khabar angin tentang kematian aneh, dia bertemu 3 pelajar kolej di sana untuk menangkap peristiwa yang dikhabarkan dan menyedari mereka terperangkap

programme.title: The Invoking
programme.desc: Selepas mewarisi rumah daripada keluarga yang tidak pernah dikenalinya, Samantha Harris (Trin Miller) dan tiga rakannya menuju ke Sader Ridge luar bandar untuk memeriksa harta itu. Tidak lama selepas tiba, Sam mula mengalami penglihatan mengerikan tentang kekejaman ganas dan kejahatan yang tidak terkata. Diganggu oleh kuasa jahat yang mengepungnya, Sam mengalami mimpi ngeri apabila syaitan dari masa lalunya enggan terus dikebumikan lagi.

programme.title: Bodyguard Ep20
programme.desc: Memaparkan Shamsul masih syak bapa tirinya Kamal bukan lelaki yang baik, Farish menasihat agar menerima kehidupan bapa tiri seadanya. Salina pula didapati bukan kekasih Kamal, dia sebenarnya gadis suruhan (call girl) untuk melayani klien Kamal. dalam perniagaannya. Ryan rakan sekampung Salina menasihatnya supaya berhenti melakukan pekerjaan tersebut. Shamsul pula cuba ditembak oleh seseorang semasa bersama-sama dengan Farish. Shamsul syak Kamal yang merancang pembunuhan tersebut kerana dia anak tunggal dalam keluarganya. Kematiannya akan memboleh Kamal menguasai harta keluarganya. Siasatan oleh Farish mendapati Pak Long Shamsul yang merancangpembunuhan tersebut. Bakri, bodyguard kepada Sarrah mendapati mereka diekori oleh Taufik. Berlaku pergaduhan yang akhirnya Taufik tertangkap.

programme.title: Howl
programme.desc: Apabila penumpang di dalam kereta api diserang oleh makhluk, mereka mesti bersatu untuk bertahan sehingga pagi.

programme.title: The Cave
programme.desc: Apabila pasukan bola sepak remaja yang terdiri daripada 12 lelaki, berumur 11-16, dan jurulatih mereka berusia 25 tahun terperangkap jauh di dalam gua di Utara Thailand, beribu-ribu sukarelawan dan tentera dari seluruh dunia bersatu dalam perlumbaan melawan masa untuk mencari mereka . Sebaik sahaja kanak-kanak lelaki itu ditemui hidup sepuluh hari kemudian, satu-satunya jalan keluar ialah berenang selama lima jam yang mustahil yang hanya penyelam gua yang pakar boleh bertahan. Di Ireland, juruelektrik kilang kapal terbang dan penyelam gua rekreasi Jim Warny menerima panggilan: "Berapa lama lagi anda boleh berada di sini?" Tiba di Thailand, Jim melangkah keluar dari pesawat dan masuk ke dalam guamisi tiga hari bermata pisau sedang dijalankan. Berdasarkan peristiwa sebenar, THE CAVE menceritakan kisah mendebarkan tentang misi menyelamat antarabangsa terbesar pada zaman moden, dari perspektif unik lelaki dan wanita yang menghadapi keputusan hidup dan mati dan mempamerkan keazaman dan pengorbanan yang tidak mementingkan diri sendiri, yang memuncak dengan keputusan yang berjaya menentang semua kemungkinan.

programme.title: Plan B Ep1
programme.desc: Episod pertama ini mengisahkan Khai dan Airis kedua-dua mereka daripada keluarga kaya mempertaruhkan wang dalam satu perlumbaan haram kereta "drift". Airis memenangi perlumbaan itu dengan imbuhan wang sebanyak RM20 ribu. Khai tidak berpuas hati, kerana Airis yang dikatakan baru dalam aktiviti ini dengan mudah mengalahkannya. Khai meneruskan usahanya untuk berkenalan dengan Airis dengan bantuan rakanya, Que mendapatkan butir peribadi, Airis menerusi laman sosial "FB".

programme.title: Born To Fight
programme.desc: Daew ialah seorang polis yang telah menangkap penyerang jahat Jeneral Yang, tetapi pasangannya terbunuh dalam kes itu dan Daew menjadi tertekan. Bagaimanapun, kakaknya meminta dia menyertainya dan beberapa rakan atletnya ke sebuah kampung kecil untuk memberi makanan dan mainan kepada penduduk kampung. Apa yang bermula sebagai perjalanan untuk membantu orang ramai bertukar menjadi mimpi ngeri apabila anak buah Yang tiba di kampung dan mengambil alih, menuntut pembebasan Yang atau peluru berpandu nuklear akan melanda Bangkok. Apabila penduduk kampung dibunuh kiri dan kanan, Daew dan para atlet mesti memulakan revolusi menentang kezaliman sebelum terlambat.

programme.title: Plan B Ep2
programme.desc: Episod ke-2 mengisahkan Khai berjaya memujuk Airis menemankannya minum setelah membawanya bersiar-siar melihat suasana Kuala Lumpur dari udara dengan kapal terbang jenis ringan miliknya. Que pula seorang pelajar kolej salah seorang daripada rakan Khai sedang diintip dan diekori polis. Kemudian Airis bersetuju berlumba kereta secara haram dengan Khai, sebagai satu syarat untuk keluar bagi kali kedua bersama-sama minum dengannya. Setelah Khai memenangi perlumbaan kereta iru, Airis seterusnya mencabar Khai supaya melakukan aktiviti yang lebih mencabar, iaitu mencuri kereta, kononnya sematamata sebagai satu hiburan sahaja.

programme.title: Haq
programme.desc: "Haq" ialah sebuah filem aksi mengenai perjuangan antara kebaikan dan kejahatan.Haq (Zul Huzaimy) dan Bad (Adi Putra) dikurniakan kuasa istimewa.Bad, yang menjadi anak angkat oleh keluarga Haq, mempunyai kebencian yang mendalam terhadap Haq.Dia menggunakan kuasanya untuk mencemarkan nama baik Haq.Bagaimanapun, Haq enggan menggunakan kuasanya untuk menghalang Bad sehingga dia mendapati dirinya terperangkap oleh yang terakhir.

programme.title: Pipeline
programme.desc: Semasa pengusir setan Do-jin menuju ke pusat komuniti terbiar dengan khabar angin tentang kematian aneh, dia bertemu 3 pelajar kolej di sana untuk menangkap peristiwa yang dikhabarkan dan menyedari mereka terperangkap

programme.title: Mantera Anjasmoro Ep6
programme.desc: Episod ini mengisahkan ilmu yang Sabrina dapatkan dari Ramona, sangat berkesan kerana kehidupan Suria semakin tidak tenteram dan asyik diganggu oleh mahluk yang ganjil. Dia juga menjadi semakin agresif sehingga menolak nasihat ibunya. Sementarai itu, Zahid semakin mesra dengan Sabrina serta menurut kata-kata Sabrina, dia juga berjanji akan menceraikan Suria. Zahid masih tidak sedar yang Sabrina dilindungi oleh bomoh Ramona.

programme.title: Howl
programme.desc: Apabila penumpang di dalam kereta api diserang oleh makhluk, mereka mesti bersatu untuk bertahan sehingga pagi.

programme.title: Arjuna Ep5
programme.desc: Arjuna cuba difitnah melakukan perkara sumbang oleh Amutra dan kawan-kawannya. Mereka ingin membawa Arjuna menghadap ke pengadilan tetapi berlaku pergelutan, di mana Jagat iaitu sepupu kepada Amutra tidak sengaja menikam Amutra kemudian melarikan diri.

programme.title: Jodoh Syaitan
programme.desc: Megat pulang ke kampungnya untuk dinikahkan dengan wanita pilihan ibunya, kerana dia terlalu kerap gagal mencari pasangan hidupnya sendiri. Sementara itu, rakan-rakannya di sana, Awang dan Kulup, ditugaskan oleh Tok Chai untuk mencari mayat untuk dihidupkan semula dan menjadi isteri Tok Chai.

programme.title: Kampung Drift
programme.desc: Menggabungkan aksi, komedi dan sci-fi, Kampung Drift ialah kisah kedewasaan bergenre silang Johan, seorang remaja yang mencari erti kehidupan dan cinta melalui perlumbaan drift.

programme.title: Santau Merasuk Ep1
programme.desc: Episod 1 mengisahkan lelaki tua Mafrub mengamuk, menyumpah seranah Halim dan cuba menghalang sebuah jentolak dari menumbangkan sebatang pokok jejawi di kawasan pembinaan. Sebelum itu Mahrub memuja pokok tersebut sambil berkata-kata dan memujuk penunggu pokok itu. Mafrub rebah mati seiring dengan pokok jejawi itu tumbang ke bumi.

programme.title: Jodoh Syaitan
programme.desc: Megat pulang ke kampungnya untuk dinikahkan dengan wanita pilihan ibunya, kerana dia terlalu kerap gagal mencari pasangan hidupnya sendiri. Sementara itu, rakan-rakannya di sana, Awang dan Kulup, ditugaskan oleh Tok Chai untuk mencari mayat untuk dihidupkan semula dan menjadi isteri Tok Chai.

programme.title: Busut Bonang
programme.desc: Joey, pemilik rancangan televisyen "Merungkai Misteri", telah dipanggil ke Kampung Bonang untuk menyiasat misteri kematian ngeri Cikgu Hassan. Berikutan kematiannya, penduduk kampung mendakwa rohnya kelihatan berkeliaran di kampung mencari pengganti baru. Pada masa yang sama, anak perempuannya Julia sering tidak sihat sekarang kerana diganggu oleh makhluk ghaib. Untuk membersihkan nama Cikgu Hassan, Joey menculik Lufty, seorang lelaki yang tanpa disedari terlibat dalam perkara ini semasa mencari pekerjaan, untuk menjadi krunya semasa siasatan. Misteri semakin mendalam apabila Joey dan Lufty, disertai Julia, diganggu oleh semangat Penunggu Busut ketika dalam perjalanan ke Busut dan mereka tersesat.

programme.title: Arjuna Ep3
programme.desc: Yo bergegas ke balai raya lalu memukul beduk untuk mengalihkan perhatian penduduk kampung yang sedang di panggang di atas bara api yang besar. Dengan lantas, Asya diselamatkan dan dia memberitahu bahawa sikap penduduk tiba-tiba berubah kerana sebenarnya kuasa jahat sudah menguasai diri dan fikiran mereka.

programme.title: Arjuna Ep4
programme.desc: Gabungan para pendekar sakti melawan Lang Kajai dan Nading menyebabkan mereka mundur dan kabur. Arjuna bermeditasi di bawah kawalan Dzulkarnain untuk mengenali masa silamnya di mana dia ialah anak kepada pasangan pendekar sakti dan dirinya mempunyai keistimewaan.

programme.title: Hantu Tenggek
programme.desc: Sekumpulan penipu yang diketuai oleh Tariq yang berpura-pura mengusir tempat berhantu telah diperas ugut oleh Tuan Sidek, seorang pemaju bangunan. Mereka perlu meyakinkan pesaing Tuan Sidek bahawa bangunan tertentu berhantu apabila mereka terperangkap di dalamnya. Kecuali mereka tidak perlu meyakinkan kerana bangunan itu benar-benar dihantui oleh roh yang tidak tenteram. Roh memerlukan bantuan mereka untuk memenuhi hasrat terakhirnya

programme.title: Arjuna Ep5
programme.desc: Arjuna cuba difitnah melakukan perkara sumbang oleh Amutra dan kawan-kawannya. Mereka ingin membawa Arjuna menghadap ke pengadilan tetapi berlaku pergelutan, di mana Jagat iaitu sepupu kepada Amutra tidak sengaja menikam Amutra kemudian melarikan diri.

programme.title: Rumah Pasung
programme.desc: Ryan, Sultan dan Mayang merupakan krew program tv tersebut. Suatu hari Ryan terpaksa menghadiri pengebumian bapa kandungnya. Ibu bapa Ryan membongkar masa lalu Ryan. Ryan anak angkat. Ayah Ryan meninggalkan sebuah rumah untuknya.

programme.title: Dendam Orang Mati
programme.desc: Lena (Lisa Surihani) tersedar dari koma selama dua tahun dan hilang ingatan akibat kemalangan. Keadaan bertambah mengelirukan apabila diperkenalkan kepada isteri baru Shahrul (Fizz Fairuz), Min (Miera Leyana) di flat lamanya di tingkat 4 yang kini menjadi tingkat 3A. Lena mula mengesyaki sesuatu yang buruk telah berlaku flat tersebut dan mula berdepan dengan kejadian-kejadian aneh yang menyeramkan. Gangguan seram ini memberikan lebih tekanan terhadap Lena yang terasa diabaikan oleh suaminya, Shahrul yang berbelah bahagi antara isteri mudanya dan Lena.

programme.title: Mantera Anjasmoro Ep7
programme.desc: Episod ini mengisahkan keadaan Suria semakin teruk dan bertindak ganas seperti dirasuk hantu. Zahid juga jarang datang menengok Suria. Bomoh wanita yang membuat santau untuk Suria juga mati dalam keadaan ngeri. Bapa meminta bantuan Ustaz Ibrahim, dalam perjalanan untuk membantu Suria, uztas pula terkorban dalam kemalangan jalanraya. Seterusnya, Suria pula mati di hospital dalam keadaan ngeri.

programme.title: Pipeline
programme.desc: Semasa pengusir setan Do-jin menuju ke pusat komuniti terbiar dengan khabar angin tentang kematian aneh, dia bertemu 3 pelajar kolej di sana untuk menangkap peristiwa yang dikhabarkan dan menyedari mereka terperangkap

programme.title: Jangan Ikut Aku Ep2
programme.desc: Akil yang dihinggap sakit gatal-gatal pulang ke kampung untuk mencari penawar. Akil berubat dengan bomoh Tok Misai dan juga diberi sebentuk cincin permata hijau. Malangnya keesokan hari, Tok Misai terbunuh semasa berkelahi dengan Pawang Anjang Itam yang sedang mencari cincin 4 keramat yang berada dalam milik Tok Misai. Sepulangnya ke bandar, Akil dapati gatal-gatalnya hilang dan diberitahu kepada kawannya Nabil. Nabil mengingatkan Akil supaya berjaga-jaga kerana kebiasaannya Tok Bomoh ada membela hantu. Akil mula percaya cakap Nabil kerana dia pernah diusik oleh lembaga pada waktu malam. Akil pulang sekali lagi ke kampung untuk menemui Tok Misai tetapi diberitahu Tok Misai telah mati terbunuh. Di masa sama Siti anak Tok Misai sedang mencari siapa yang terakhir berubat dengan ayahnya.

programme.title: Arjuna Ep6
programme.desc: Amurta yang dalam keadaan nazak diselamatkan oleh Arjuna menggunakan kuasa sakti dan Amutra sembuh tanpa meninggalkan sedikit kesan pun pada badannya. Orang Kaya Sadhya muncul bersama Jagat, dengan beberapa orang untuk menangkap Arjuna tetapi dihalang oleh Amutra yang memberitahu kisah yang sebenar tetapi Orang Kaya Sadhya tidak peduli dan membawa pulang Amurta.

programme.title: Laddaland
programme.desc: Apabila sebuah keluarga berpindah ke Laddaland, sebuah pembangunan perumahan mewah dengan rumah yang besar dan cantik, mereka mendapati kehidupan di kawasan kejiranan baharu mereka tidak begitu sempurna apabila mereka menghadapi satu siri peristiwa paranormal yang menakutkan yang mendorong keluarga itu ke tepi kegilaan. Ini ialah penerangan ringkas tentang kandungan.

programme.title: Driving School
programme.desc: Perasaan cemburu dan curiga menyebabkan Maimunah, isteri kepada Dato' Zaqlol mengambil kelas memandu di sekolah tempat suaminya mendaftarkan diri bersama perempuan simpanannya, Sally. Namun, terjadinya salah faham apabila Maimunah menganggap bahawa Faridah ialah perempuan simpanan suaminya. Hilmi, seorang guru memandu dan juga kekasih Faridah cuba digoda Maimunah.

programme.title: Suci Dalam Debu
programme.desc: Roy, seorang anak kaya yang ingin berkawan dengan pemuzik bertemu Rina di sebuah kelab malam. Namun, Rina telah ditunangkan dengan Tengku Johan oleh bapanya, Tengku Aziz. Tengku Johan ingin mempercepatkan tarikh perkahwinan mereka kerana ingin memiliki Rina. Roy telah dicabar dan diletakkan taruhan oleh Tengku Johan jika benar dia boleh mendapatkan Rina.

programme.title: Mira Edora
programme.desc: Mira Edora telah jatuh cinta kepada gurunya tanpa mengetahui hubungan silam gurunya itu bersama ibunya, Hapipah. Dapatkah hubungan mereka terus berkekalan setelah rahsia itu terbongkar?

programme.title: Wanita Bertudung Hitam
programme.desc: Maya, gadis kampung bertukar menjadi seorang model terkenal di ibu kota, Kuala Lumpur. Dilimpahi kesenangan dan kekayaan, Maya menukar nama menjadi Tiara, seorang gadis yang glamor. Tertimpa kemalangan, dia mula menjadi murung dan melupakan kehidupan lamanya serta menukar kembali ke nama asalnya. Dia mula membaiki hubungannya dengan Tuhan dan mempelajari agama.

programme.title: Driving School
programme.desc: Perasaan cemburu dan curiga menyebabkan Maimunah, isteri kepada Dato' Zaqlol mengambil kelas memandu di sekolah tempat suaminya mendaftarkan diri bersama perempuan simpanannya, Sally. Namun, terjadinya salah faham apabila Maimunah menganggap bahawa Faridah ialah perempuan simpanan suaminya. Hilmi, seorang guru memandu dan juga kekasih Faridah cuba digoda Maimunah.

programme.title: Cinta Kita
programme.desc: Patah hati setelah dicurangi teman lelakinya, Remy, Latifah mengubah penampilannya menjadi seorang 'tomboy'. Sukar untuknya mempercayai lelaki, dia pun berpindah ke tempat lain. Perkenalannya bersama Arman, seorang penulis novel mengubah kembali cara Latifah yeng berpenampilan lelaki. Hubungan mereka yang semakin rapat menimbulkan perasaan cinta.

programme.title: Ringgit Kassorga
programme.desc: Kekayaan, kemewahan dan hawa nafsu - semuanya boleh didapati di Pulau Kasorrga. Pulau khas buat warga elit ini menjadi tempat buat orang kaya untuk mencari ketenangan dan kepuasan. Pemilik syarikat permodelan dan pencari bakat, Meera Almeida membekalkan gadis ke pulau itu dan dibayar wang komisen yang tinggi. Namun rahsia gelap Pulau Kasorrga mula diungkai sedikit demi sedikit.

programme.title: Nadia
programme.desc: Nadia mengikut ayahnya yang baru bersara daripada menjadi pegawai kedutaan Malaysia di London pulang ke Malaysia. Namun ibunya enggan pulang dan masih tinggal di London. Nadia memulakan pengajiannya di ITM dan menjalin persahabatan dengan seorang pemuda bernama Izam. Apabila Nadia mendapati ayahnya mempunyai hubungan intim dengan seorang janda kaya, dia berikrar untuk mengambil ibunya kembali serta memulihkan hubungan keluarganya yang terputus itu.

programme.title: Amok
programme.desc: Amukan seorang lelaki yang dikejutkan dengan pertembungan budaya kebaratan yang mendorong anak Melayu berperwatakan liar. Wan Man, pelajar ilmu silat terperangkap dalam satu hubungan cinta bersama gadis Amerika, Natalie. Gadis liar yang mengamalkan gaya hidup bebas mula mempengaruhi rakan Wan Man. Segala ajaran Pak Guru terhadap Wan Man dan pusaka batin warisan bapanya mula menggangu perasaannya.

programme.title: Abang 92
programme.desc: Kematian kedua ibu bapa yang tidak disangka, Imran harus memikul amanah mereka untuk menjaga adik-adiknya. Syarikat milik bapanya ingin dikuasai oleh pakcik-pakciknya yang menyeleweng wang milik syarikat, Imran yang tidak ingin perkara itu berlaku mula melakukan sesuatu. Seorang peguam jelita ditugaskan untuk membantunya - bermulalah kisah cinta di antara mereka berdua.

programme.title: Perempuan, Isteri dan ....
programme.desc: Zaleha berkahwin lari ke Thailand bersama seorang lelaki lain menyebabkan bakal suaminya, Amir mula menjejakinya. Tragedi berlaku apabila Amir membunuh suami Zaleha dan menjualnya kepada seorang bapa ayam di Thailand. Diperdaya oleh Amir, mereka berdua akhirnya menikah - namun Zaleha mempunyai rancangan lain iaitu untuk membalas dendam atas apa yang telah dilakukan terhadapnya.

programme.title: Harry Boy
programme.desc: Kurang kasih sayang dan perhatian dari keluarga, Harry Boy mula menagih kasih di luar. Dia bertemu Julia dan mula terikut-ikut gaya hidup Julia yang bebas. Ini mendatangkan kerisauan terhadap ibu dan bapanya apabila dia mula tidak menghadiri kelas dan pulang ke rumah. Kemudian, dia bertemu pula dengan Haryati yang telah mengubahnya menjadi manusia yang lebih baik.

programme.title: Hati Bukan Kristal
programme.desc: Seorang wartawan yang bercita-cita tinggi, Nina, amat mengagumi dan menyukai hasil karya seorang wartawan dan editor bernama Cik Ida. Meskipun baru sahaja menceburi bidang kewartawanan di Harian Nasional namun sikapnya yang lain daripada yang lain telah mencuri perhatian ramai. Razief memandang rendah terhadap Nina namun perasaan kasih mula terdetik di hati. Michelle dengan kerjaya gelapnya terpaksa menghadapi pelbagai cabaran yang mendorongnya untuk melakukan tindakan drastik yang berbahaya.

programme.title: Cinta Kita
programme.desc: Patah hati setelah dicurangi teman lelakinya, Remy, Latifah mengubah penampilannya menjadi seorang 'tomboy'. Sukar untuknya mempercayai lelaki, dia pun berpindah ke tempat lain. Perkenalannya bersama Arman, seorang penulis novel mengubah kembali cara Latifah yeng berpenampilan lelaki. Hubungan mereka yang semakin rapat menimbulkan perasaan cinta.

programme.title: Hati Bukan Kristal
programme.desc: Seorang wartawan yang bercita-cita tinggi, Nina, amat mengagumi dan menyukai hasil karya seorang wartawan dan editor bernama Cik Ida. programme.title: Suci Dalam Debu
programme.desc: Roy, seorang anak kaya yang ingin berkawan dengan pemuzik bertemu Rina di sebuah kelab malam. Namun, Rina telah ditunangkan dengan Tengku Johan oleh bapanya, Tengku Aziz. Tengku Johan ingin mempercepatkan tarikh perkahwinan mereka kerana ingin memiliki Rina. Roy telah dicabar dan diletakkan taruhan oleh Tengku Johan jika benar dia boleh mendapatkan Rina.

programme.title: Amok
programme.desc: Amukan seorang lelaki yang dikejutkan dengan pertembungan budaya kebaratan yang mendorong anak Melayu berperwatakan liar. Wan Man, pelajar ilmu silat terperangkap dalam satu hubungan cinta bersama gadis Amerika, Natalie. Gadis liar yang mengamalkan gaya hidup bebas mula mempengaruhi rakan Wan Man. Segala ajaran Pak Guru terhadap Wan Man dan pusaka batin warisan bapanya mula menggangu perasaannya.

programme.title: Driving School
programme.desc: Perasaan cemburu dan curiga menyebabkan Maimunah, isteri kepada Dato' Zaqlol mengambil kelas memandu di sekolah tempat suaminya mendaftarkan diri bersama perempuan simpanannya, Sally. Namun, terjadinya salah faham apabila Maimunah menganggap bahawa Faridah ialah perempuan simpanan suaminya. Hilmi, seorang guru memandu dan juga kekasih Faridah cuba digoda Maimunah.

programme.title: Perempuan, Isteri dan ....
programme.desc: Zaleha berkahwin lari ke Thailand bersama seorang lelaki lain menyebabkan bakal suaminya, Amir mula menjejakinya. Tragedi berlaku apabila Amir membunuh suami Zaleha dan menjualnya kepada seorang bapa ayam di Thailand. Diperdaya oleh Amir, mereka berdua akhirnya menikah - namun Zaleha mempunyai rancangan lain iaitu untuk membalas dendam atas apa yang telah dilakukan terhadapnya.

programme.title: Wanita Bertudung Hitam
programme.desc: Maya, gadis kampung bertukar menjadi seorang model terkenal di ibu kota, Kuala Lumpur. Dilimpahi kesenangan dan kekayaan, Maya menukar nama menjadi Tiara, seorang gadis yang glamor. Tertimpa kemalangan, dia mula menjadi murung dan melupakan kehidupan lamanya serta menukar kembali ke nama asalnya. Dia mula membaiki hubungannya dengan Tuhan dan mempelajari agama.

programme.title: Abang 92
programme.desc: Kematian kedua ibu bapa yang tidak disangka, Imran harus memikul amanah mereka untuk menjaga adik-adiknya. Syarikat milik bapanya ingin dikuasai oleh pakcik-pakciknya yang menyeleweng wang milik syarikat, Imran yang tidak ingin perkara itu berlaku mula melakukan sesuatu. Seorang peguam jelita ditugaskan untuk membantunya - bermulalah kisah cinta di antara mereka berdua.

programme.title: Mira Edora
programme.desc: Mira Edora telah jatuh cinta kepada gurunya tanpa mengetahui hubungan silam gurunya itu bersama ibunya, Hapipah. Dapatkah hubungan mereka terus berkekalan setelah rahsia itu terbongkar?

programme.title: Harry Boy
programme.desc: Kurang kasih sayang dan perhatian dari keluarga, Harry Boy mula menagih kasih di luar. Dia bertemu Julia dan mula terikut-ikut gaya hidup Julia yang bebas. Ini mendatangkan kerisauan terhadap ibu dan bapanya apabila dia mula tidak menghadiri kelas dan pulang ke rumah. Kemudian, dia bertemu pula dengan Haryati yang telah mengubahnya menjadi manusia yang lebih baik.

Pemilik syarikat permodelan dan pencari bakat, Meera Almeida membekalkan gadis ke pulau itu dan dibayar wang komisen yang tinggi. Namun rahsia gelap Pulau Kasorrga mula diungkai sedikit demi sedikit.

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa(T) Ep170
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: Stories In Taiwan (T) Ep1020
programme.desc: In a playful and relaxed style, the host went deep into the corners of various towns and villages in Taiwan, looking for the uniqueness, introduced the special local customs and traditions.

programme.title: Detective Chinatown 3
programme.desc: After the events in Bangkok and New York, Tang Ren and Qin Feng are invited to solve a murder case in Tokyo, but it turns out to be a challenge for the worlds best detectives. While the case has become complicated and confusing since the worlds top detective Q got involved, a hilarious challenge for the best detectives in Asia has just begun

programme.title: Mr McDreamy
programme.desc: A second generation rich man squanders his parents money and calls himself Mr McDreamy. When his parents finally have enough and cut him off financially, he establishes a Mr McDreamy Training Academy using various unconventional means to transform his four recruits into Mr McDreamies with hilarious results.

programme.title: Invisible Target
programme.desc: Three young police officers driven by different motives decide to join forces to defeat Tien and his lethal, mercenary gang. As they team up to prevent another massive robbery, they discover that it is instigated by another unknown man. With courage, wits and dexterity, the trio are determined to not let Tien and the instigator escape.

programme.title: The New Big Boss
programme.desc: A young man seeks out the Wolf, a legendary undefeated warrior. When he sees that the Wolf is now an old man, he prompts him to retell his past glories.

programme.title: I'm Livin' It
programme.desc: Once a successful banker, Bowen now spends his nights in a 24-hour fast food joint where he meets a group of homeless people. Together they strive to get themselves out of rock bottom.

programme.title: The White Storm
programme.desc: Three Narcotics Bureau officers who are good friends get involved in a case with the drug lord. When the operation fails, they must make a devastating decision - two can live, but one must die. Five years later, the two vow to take revenge but end up competing against each other for their own lives. Will brotherhood be sacrificed again?

programme.title: Let It Ghost
programme.desc: The movie consists of three urban ghost stories: when a film crew is haunted by a ghost, the director decides to cast her to play the ghost; when a taxi driver takes his girlfriend to a staycation, a horny ghost adds spice to it; a wandering child ghost refuses to leave a mall that is to be demolished, so the tenants help her to move on.

programme.title: Book of Love
programme.desc: A casino PR in Macau receives a classic novel 84, Charing Cross Road. She sends back the novel with a letter to where it came from as she does not like it. A real estate agent in California receives the novel and as it does not belong to him, he sends it back with a letter as well. The two form a relationship after all the back and forth.

programme.title: My Kickass Wife
programme.desc: Jade is a beautiful royal guard who is set up for marriage by the Queen in order to avoid the King setting eyes on her. Jade falls for Sean and helps him win the contest for her. After the wedding, Sean discovers her bad temper and visits a brothel in his despair. He meets and is attracted to a girl there, not knowing she has a secret agenda...

programme.title: Men Suddenly in Love
programme.desc: Five high-school alumni - councilor Ng Yuk Yan (Eric Tsang), actor Cheung Chau Wan (Jim Chim), gynecologist Fu Mo Sum (Wong Jing), feng shui master Szeto Kei Fung (Chapman To), and dance coach Charlie Lam (Det Dik) - get together to throw a birthday party for their respected teacher Mr. Chu (Richard Ng), who enlightened them about the birds and the bees. Five delectable young models appear at the party, during which the 80-year-old educator gets too excited and unfortunately kicks the bucket - but not before telling his pupils to fulfill his last wish and get a little naughty! The quintet of married men then takes it upon themselves to conquer the babes, all the while trying to evade the watchful eye of their wives (Maggie Cheung Ho Yee, Yeung Sze Man, Monica Chan, Mak Ling Ling, and Jacqueline Chong).

programme.title: Lion Rock
programme.desc: Based on the true story of David Ki, one of Asias top rock climbers who lost everything when a motorcycle accident crippled him. Rather than succumbing to his fate, David found a way of scaling the dizzying peaks again by becoming a wheelchair-bound athlete and soon reached the peak of Lion Rock!

programme.title: Cyber Heist
programme.desc: Hackers have caused a large-scale cyber attack, but luckily cyber security engineer Chun, manages to fend it off with his protective firewall system. To Chun's surprise, his boss is the mastermind of the attack, and when Chun gets trapped in a money laundering operation, he must fight against his boss in the cyber world to prove his innocence.

programme.title: One Second
programme.desc: Directed by renowned director Zhang Yimou, the film is set during the Cultural Revolution, where a common man escapes a labour camp to find a newsreel that captures his daughter for one second in a movie. On the way, he encounters an orphan who also seeks the movie reel. Can the man finally pass the reel to a projectionist and screen the movie?

programme.title: Seobok
programme.desc: Former secret agent Ki Hun is entrusted with a secret mission to escort the first human clone, Seobok, to a safe place. Seobok, who possesses a life-preserving DNA that could save humanity, explores the outside world with Ki Hun for the first time but they are both chased and claimed as terrorists by CIA. How can Ki Hun protect Seobok from danger?

programme.title: Deception of the Novelist
programme.desc: This is a sexy thriller adapted from the hit story by the famous internet author, Xxharuki. A self-help book author Xu lives happily with his wife Jeana and their son. However, when a voluptuous and seductive tenant rents their apartment upstairs, Xus life is turned upside down.

programme.title: Two Tigers
programme.desc: This crime comedy is about a bumbling young man Fang Nan, who kidnaps a middle-aged businessman Zhang Cheng Gong for ransom. However, the captor becomes the captive when Zhang turns the tables on Fang and forces him to complete three tasks. The two men soon find themselves sharing a journey filled with absurdity and deception.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon II: Wild Wild Bunch
programme.desc: Starring four Hong Kong Film Awards Best Actors, Simon Yam, Louis Koo, Tony Leung Ka Fai and Gordon Lam, this action-thriller follows the real-life kidnapping events that terrorized Hong Kongs elite in the 1990s by serial billionaire-kidnapper Logan and his gang.

programme.title: Black Ransom
programme.desc: Mann, an accomplished police officer, has allowed his career to wane after his wife was murdered by the mafia. However, Mann is forced to return to his former glory when he is assigned to investigate a former police inspector suspected to be kidnapping mafia bosses and demanding ransoms in exchange for their lives.

programme.title: Concerto of the Bully
programme.desc: The story follows an internet songwriter Jamie, who is gifted with an extraordinary retentive memory. One day, she was kidnapped by Yung, a street punk, to a remote fish raft. In the hope to flee with the only ability she has, Jamie offers to give Yung a spiritual music therapy. The two who have nothing in common begin to form a bond through music.

programme.title: A Chinese Fairy Tale
programme.desc: Young demon hunter Yan loves the fox spirit Xiao Qian but has to rid her memories of him as a human cannot love a demon. Years later, Ning meets Xiao Qian and they fall in love. Yan advises Ning to give Xiao Qian up as she is now controlled by an evil Tree Demon but he refuses. As the Tree Demon seeks revenge, Xiao Qian also starts to remember Yan.

programme.title: The Fatal Raid
programme.desc: Twenty years after a deadly bloodbath between the Hong Kong Police and Macau gangsters, Madam Fong, the surviving team member, leads a new squad of four policewomen across borders to pursue young anarchists terrorizing Macau in a mission to protect the Hong Kong Polices Deputy Chief Commissioner.

programme.title: Tales from the Occult
programme.desc: The movie consists of three tales about the horrors lurking in dark corners of the city. A young pop star goes back into depression when spooky things happen in her new home; an online influencer performs live in a mall, but it ends up being a livestream of his death; the residents of a tenement building battle a mysterious figure in the stairwell.

programme.title: Hello Babies
programme.desc: Lui Ming and Yeung Wai are constantly fighting with each other on everything, and now they are competing to be the first to get a grandson. Lui hires the Super Star midwife Gong San to supervise their sons and nephews to make it happen

programme.title: The Trough
programme.desc: Yu Chau is a cop who has gone very deeply undercover within the triads. When he accidentally kills one of his pals in an operation, he runs off into the wild to lick his wounds. Upon his return, he teams up with fellow officers Jim and Jackie to catch a triad Boss, only to unveil collusion with government officials at the highest level.

programme.title: The Three Swordsmen
programme.desc: Knife, Jian and Sam are three famous swordsmen. Knife works for the Emperor and when Sam is framed for murdering the Empress, Knife gets involved. Sam manages to find the murderer but is injured in the process. This however did not stop him fighting Jian for the top spot in the martial arts world.

programme.title: Knockout
programme.desc: A former boxing champion and convict who has just been released from prison discovers that his wife has died and he is now a single parent. The situation is made worse with his daughters diagnosis of leukaemia. In order to encourage his daughter and fulfil his promise of never giving up, he re-enters the boxing ring.

programme.title: Princess & 7 Kung Fu Masters
programme.desc: Seven Kung Fu masters live in Lucky Town, the only safe residing place in northeast China. When warlord Lam refuses to side with the Japanese, an agent is assigned to take over his army and kill his daughter using ninjutsu. Lams daughter escapes and seeks help from the seven masters, who finally defeat the enemy and save the warlord!

programme.title: The Infernal Walker
programme.desc: Ting is an undercover police who infiltrates a triad and Tuen is a triad mole being planted into the police force. While Tang is tired of being an undercover cop, Tuen wishes to quit the triad and become a real police. When the triad boss sets a trap to uncover the moles' identity, the two must fight for themselves.

programme.title: Raging Fire
programme.desc: As the police sets to arrest a drug lord, a team of masked thugs steals the drugs and murders the cops. Inspector Bong is devastated to see the aftermath of the carnage and soon discovers that the killers are led by Ngo, a former fellow cop who was forced into a life of crime by him. As the two men meet again, it is time to settle the score

programme.title: Let It Ghost
programme.desc: The movie consists of three urban ghost stories: when a film crew is haunted by a ghost, the director decides to cast her to play the ghost; when a taxi driver takes his girlfriend to a staycation, a horny ghost adds spice to it; a wandering child ghost refuses to leave a mall that is to be demolished, so the tenants help her to move on.

programme.title: New Police Story
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Wing is an elite in the police force but has been drowning his guilt in booze after his entire team was killed by the Gang of Five in a mission. A year later, a young rookie detective with a complicated background is assigned to partner Wing and manages to inspire him into action, as Wing vows to take down the gang.

programme.title: Missbehavior
programme.desc: A group of friends who are formerly close but now somewhat estranged, unite to help one of their own who is in trouble at work. In this hilarious comedy, the friends must find a replacement bottle of breast milk before the end of the day as chaos breaks out!

programme.title: Bodies at Rest
programme.desc: When three armed criminals barge into a morgue, a forensic doctor and his student must fight with their lives to stop the criminals from obtaining a bullet from inside a corpse that is a key piece of evidence in a deadly crime.

programme.title: The Lark
programme.desc: Sixties pop star Carrie Ku plays the "Little Lark" in this romantic-drama of mistaken identity that is a treasure trove of some of the most popular Mandarin songs of all time.

programme.title: The Golden Knight
programme.desc: The heroine Yu Fei Xia is accused of stealing the book of martial arts secrets. To prove her innocence, she disguises herself as a man and finds her way into the Shaolin Temple to find out the truth...

programme.title: Sex, Love and Hate
programme.desc: This masterpiece spins three interconnected tales about Hong Kong society's differing views on love and what women want from love. Follow a trio of Hong Kong women as they explore relationships and fulfil their hopes of finding true love.

programme.title: Five Superfighters
programme.desc: A kung fu master and his three students lost everything after they are floored by a bully. To take revenge, the students find ways to learn from other kung fu masters and come back six months later to have a rematch with the bully on their masters birthday.

programme.title: Fangs of the Cobra
programme.desc: Incredibly, the title serpent is not a harbinger of horror, but actually the film's hero. This virtuous viper sniffs out bombs, fights gangs, battles a baby-killing rodent and even takes on a duplicitous woman. This one-of-a-kind thriller will be applauded by reptile fans everywhere.

programme.title: A Deadly Secret
programme.desc: A corrupt magistrate, obsessed with finding a hidden treasure, jails and tortures his daughter's lover and buries his daughter alive! Ironically, it is in her coffin that the secret to the hidden treasure is found, setting off a frenzy of destruction.

programme.title: Fast Fingers
programme.desc: After his release from prison, Uncle Bill returns to make a fortune with his past thieving partners. They continue to prey on the unsuspecting public, but are closely watched by the upright police chief, who happens to be the boyfriend of one of Uncle Bills nieces!

programme.title: Bloody Parrot
programme.desc: A swordsman is suspected of being the thief of a treasure sent to Emperor. Through his investigation, he is led on to the trail of the supernatural Bloody Parrot. Poisonous things happen including a demonic possession, witches casting poison spells and disgusting autopsies. Then a dead constable turns into a vampire!

programme.title: Intimate Confessions of a Chinese Courtesan
programme.desc: Young Ai Nu is abducted and sold to the popular Four Seasons brothel run by the powerful and ruthless Madam Chun Yi. Ai Nu gets locked up in a dungeon due to her fiery attitude. Soon, a murder occurs within the brothel and a policeman must race against time to prevent a vicious revenge plot from reaching its blood-spattered conclusion.

programme.title: The Young Avenger
programme.desc: Liu seeks out Li to avenge his brothers death and loses an arm in the fight, vowing revenge ten years later. Li dies after asking his sister to send his daughter Bao Zhu to learn the Dragon Sword skill to avenge his death. Bao Zhu grows up to become a skilled swordswoman and meets Liu for the planned duel with her cousin Chen. Can she defeat Liu?

programme.title: The Perfumed Arrow
programme.desc: A charming Huangmei Opera title, this is the story of Fei E, a Generals daughter who grows up fooling everyone that she is a boy, including her two closest schoolmates. When she has to choose one of them to marry, how will Fei E tell them that she is a girl? To complicate matters, a girl who Fei E saves one day only wants to be married to her!

programme.title: Raw Courage
programme.desc: After the Ming Emperor is overthrown and his infant son was put in the care of the Black Dragon Society, a traitorous martial arts clan attacks the society, forcing an inexperienced pair of swordsman and swordswoman to flee with the infant. Their journey to deliver the infant to safety is filled with dangers that would require help from other allies

programme.title: One-armed Swordsman
programme.desc: Accepted to the Golden Sword School after his father sacrificed his life to save his master, Fang Kang is resented by his fellow pupils and decides to leave. His master's daughter challenges him to a fight and cuts off his arm. Fang masters the art of sword fighting with one arm and finds himself returning to the School to save his master again.

programme.title: The Voyage of Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung continues his incognito voyage to southern China. Accompanied by the minister and the imperial scholar, they have many amusing encounters in Yangzhou.

programme.title: Five Tough Guys
programme.desc: A titular gang of misfits come together to protect a patriotic general from a scheming usurper. To this end, the unlikely heroes act as the generals escorts on a dangerous journey to a distant British consulate, beset by enemies and sinister Japanese interference along the way.

programme.title: Pale Passion
programme.desc: Fa is an obsessive man who loves his wife Ah Hsia but is easily jealous and abuses her. When she leaves him one day, Fa hooks up with another woman, Hsing. A deadly triangle develops when Fa runs into Ah Hsia again and decides to win her back

programme.title: Shadow Girl
programme.desc: A young swordswoman becomes invisible during the day and a monster at night after taking her grandmas pill. She ruined the wedding of a bandit chiefs daughter using her powers and is hunted down by them for revenge. Will she escape the hunt?

programme.title: King Drummer
programme.desc: A young musician Chi Chiang is hired by the manager of a popular band when the group's drummer/leader Charlie, quits to join a rival group. The new drummer becomes an immediate hit, causing Charlie to be very jealous. Furthermore, the young drummer's mother is dead set against him having a music career.

programme.title: That Man In Chang-an
programme.desc: The Han Emperor dies and his Empress Lu seizes the ruling power. She plots to kill the heir to the throne, Liu Heng, but the masked warrior discovers her plot and tips off Liu. Liu sends his princess to Chang An to ask for help. The masked warrior protects the princess from attackers along the way and supports Liu to become the new Emperor.

programme.title: The Human Goddess
programme.desc: This is a love story between an alluring fairy, Seventh Sister, who comes down from heaven to experience life in 70s Hong Kong, and a man who is running a debt laden orphanage. A heartless tycoon plans to take over the orphanage for its land but has to deal with Seventh Sisters magical powers as she aims to protect it from falling into his hands!

programme.title: The Master Of Kung Fu
programme.desc: The famous kung fu master Wong Fei Hung teaches martial arts in Guangdong. A vicious gangster plots to harm Wongs disciples and frames him for robbery and murder. Wong has to fight against the culprit to prove his own innocence and take revenge for his disciples.

programme.title: Facets Of Love
programme.desc: Set in the Ming Dynasty, the story revolves around a brothel and the girls who work there. The film begins by following the life of a girl from a poor family, who is sold by her mother to the brothel. While she is the most beautiful of the girls and attracts many clients, the girl hopes to escape this sad way of life one day.

programme.title: The Sword And The Lute
programme.desc: In The Sword And The Lute, Kwei Wu (Jimmy Wang Yu) and his partner (Chin Ping) are on a mission to destroy the "Phoenix Lute", a deadly weapon that shoots poisonous needles up to 500 paces and which can only be destroyed by the Kan curved sword...

programme.title: Rose, Be My Love
programme.desc: Not a love triangle but a love 'rectangle', Rose, Be My Love is a romantic drama set on the eve of World War II that represents the high standards achieved by Shaw Brothers in both aspects of star power and technical polish.

programme.title: Purple Darts
programme.desc: A girl vows to take revenge for her parents who were murdered by four outlaws when she was only a baby. To do so, she trains hard at martial arts and teams up with a swordsman and a couple to finally kill them all.

programme.title: The Fastest Sword
programme.desc: Southern Swordsman Ting is named The Fastest Sword but is defeated by a street monk and has to fulfil his promise of working on stone craving with the monk for three years. Ting returns home to lead a peaceful life after that and declines all fight challenges. Even so, he is forced to fight the Northern Swordsman. Who will win finally?

programme.title: Whose Baby is in the Classroom?
programme.desc: Chen, a male teacher in an all girls high school, is stuck with a baby that isnt his and must take care of it. As he lives on the school grounds, the baby is a source of constant distraction and worry! Luckily, his class warms to the baby and helps him take care of it while he works his charm on Li Ching, an uptight teacher in the same school.

programme.title: Two Champions of Shaolin
programme.desc: Set in the Qing Dynasty, the Shaolin clan wants to overthrow Qing and restore the Ming Dynasty, while the Wudang clan is backed by the Qing government. The two renowned clans eventually set themselves up against each other, and a series of vicious fighting has just begun

programme.title: The Yellow Muffler
programme.desc: Japanese director Inoue Umetsugu takes on the glitzy world of nightclub performers in The Yellow Muffler. The film depicts the struggle of two singing sisters, Ching-ping (Irene Chen I-ling) and Pai-hung (Betty Ting Pei) and ends when they are cast in a new movie.

programme.title: The Kid With A Tattoo
programme.desc: Young Bao Tong witnesses the brutal murder of his kung fu master by a vicious villain. A large eagle tattoo on Baos chest was spotted by the killer as he escapes. Can Bao escape from the killer?

programme.title: Tragic Commitment
programme.desc: When the husband of a doctor, Tung is fatally wounded in an accident, he reveals to her about his affair with Blackie, who is impregnated with his baby. Despite the devastation of the betrayal and the eventual death of her husband, Tung is pressured by her mother-in-law into putting up with Blackie and offer $1M for her baby...

programme.title: The Killer Has No Return
programme.desc: Professional killer Lui goes to Malaysia after completing his mission of killing the big boss of a Hong Kong gang. His next target is a groom who is throwing his wedding banquet at a hotel in Chinatown. Just when Lui takes aim at his target, another victim instead of the groom is shot, and he becomes a scapegoat in this mystery assassination.

programme.title: The Emperor and the Minister
programme.desc: The ingenious imperial scholar Liu Yung always embarrasses Emperor Chien Lung with his quick wit and gift of gab. The emperor purposely sets him up to solve the seemingly unsolvable. However, Liu Yung resolves it easily with wit and style and foils the emperors plot once again.

programme.title: The Dragon Creek
programme.desc: This wuxia murder mystery film talks about a young girl whose father was ruthlessly murdered during China's early republican era. She has a list of villains who have been plotting against her father and together with her elder brother, the young girl sets out on a journey to hunt down the secret serial killer.

programme.title: Human Lanterns
programme.desc: Zhao was once defeated by Long in a duel. 7 years later, Long asks Zhao to make a unique lantern on his behalf to win the lantern contest, while Zhao plans for revenge. When Longs wife suddenly disappears one day and he hears about the story of human lanterns, Long suspects Zhao may be involved in the incident

programme.desc: Dragon Mountain: Surviving the Summit - South Africa's Drakensberg is one of the continent's most impressive landscapes. It is home to sharp climatic and ecological gradients as physical conditions change for both land-based creatures and the Raptors that swirl in the skies above.

programme.title: Wildlife ER 2 Ep3
programme.desc: Gutsy Koala - Shadow vet Bec, who patches up dog-bitten koala Rachel, and new vets Ruby and Kerryn, who soothe a pack of itchy possums. Free a pair of kookaburras trapped in a wall with rescue officer Dani and watch vet Tims squirrel glider knee surgery.

programme.title: Mysteries of the Mekong 1 Ep10
programme.desc: Vietnam: the Journey's End - The Mekong Delta is one of the largest on Earth. Formed over the last 8000 years, it fans out and discharges into the South China Sea via nine channels. These channels split and shape the coastline, creating unique habitats for a variety of animals.

programme.title: Great Parks of Africa 1 Ep4
programme.desc: Great Karoo - In the center of South Africa is an ancient landscape that was once an inland sea. Now its a mosaic of unique habitats. Life here has evolved ingenious solutions to survive. There is nowhere in South Africa quite like the Karoo National Park.

programme.title: Great Parks of Africa 1 Ep5
programme.desc: Kgalagadi Transfrontier Park - In the southern reaches of Africas great Kalahari basin, everything is made tough. Ancient rivers harbor water deep underground, and these hidden lifelines forge a fragile link to survival. This is the Kgalagadi Transfrontier Park.

programme.title: Attack and Defend 1 Ep4
programme.desc: Cold-Blooded Killers - From our point of view, cold-blooded predators are brutal, savvy, programmed killers. But from their point of view, its just another day at the butchers counter. These are some of the most fearsome predators on Earth.

programme.title: Into the Wild India 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Growing Up Gibbon - Hoolock Gibbons are true specialists of the Indian Jungle. Living in close knit family groups, youngsters must spend up to 9 years learning all the skills required to survive alone. From finding food in unusual places, to avoiding dangerous predators and mastering the acrobatics required for a life in the trees, we follow Samar as he finally comes of age and takes his first step into the wild.

programme.title: Wildlife Icons 2 Ep4
programme.desc: Killer Packs - Surviving in the African savanna requires wit and guile, especially for two of its hunters: African wild dogs and dwarf mongooses. These two enigmatic species live in packs and rely on well-coordinated teamwork to succeed. From looking after youngsters to finding food and warding off enemies, both species rely on their tight-knit families to overcome the challenges of everyday life.

programme.title: Wild Rockies 1 Ep5
programme.desc: Group Survival - For a great many species, the structures of group living are the most important for survival. Although social living is integral to many of the animals that call the Rocky Mountains home, no two species organize their society in the same way. Even among closely related species there can be drastic differences in social structure; communication, hierarchy, mating, and diet are all inextricably informed by specific environmental and genetic adaptations for group survival.

programme.title: Attack and Defend 1 Ep6
programme.desc: Water Warriors - From powerful sharks to mysterious and beautiful fish shoals, the underwater dynamic between predator and prey continues. Evolution is on display in these clever creatures as they use all their skills to survive.

programme.title: Ol Pejeta Diaries 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Africa Titans - The death of a wild black rhino after a fight with another dominant male, and a 14-year-old blind black rhino becomes the new ambassador for the species.

programme.title: Into the Wild India 1 Ep2
programme.desc: Land of the Secret Rhino - The grasslands of Northeast India are one of the most fertile habitats on earth. Hundreds of species of tall grass flourish here, allowing one of Indias most iconic creatures to thrive the Greater One-horned Rhino. This is one of the last places on earth where this gentle giant survives. Rani, an adult female has just had a baby, Rajah. This young rhino calf is only 3-month-old and his mom is his teacher, for the first year and half of his life. Rajah has much to learn, as he gets to grips with the world around him and everything there is to know about being a rhino.

programme.title: Wildlife Icons 2 Ep5
programme.desc: Living Together - A complex web of relationships rules all life on earth: all species are interconnected, none can survive in isolation. While some relationships are one-sided, others are mutually beneficial. From loose associations to tight-knit partnerships, everything has a place in natures great scheme. Complex interactions between species are not even limited to animals, and some of the best examples occur in the lush mountain forests of Africa.

programme.title: Orangutan Jungle School 1 Ep1
programme.desc: And So it Begins - Head to the heart of Central Kalimantan, Borneo - home to one of the most unique schools in the world. There are 68 students in all, including class clown Valentino (who loves a short-cut) and class couple Darril and Liti (who have their first fight).

programme.title: Great Blue Wild 3 Ep4
programme.desc: Life in the Food Chain - The ocean sprawls across 70 percent of our planet and is home to as many as one million known species of plants and animals. However, it is the smallest of ocean creatures that underpins the worlds largest food web plankton. These microscopic organisms drift through the oceans diverse habitats, triggering feeding cycles in their wake. Without them, life in the ocean would cease to exist.

programme.title: Ol Pejeta Diaries 1 Ep3
programme.desc: White Rhinos of Enasoit - The conservation team attempts to move two white rhinos to Ol Pejeta from the nearby Enasoit ranch after it is discovered that poachers have been watching the animals.

programme.title: Into the Wild India 1 Ep3
programme.desc: Wild Stallions of the Himalayas - The high altitude Ladakh plateau in northwest India is a land of extremes. The air is thin and the mountain landscape treacherous; winters are freezing, while summers are scorching hot. The Tibetan wild ass is king of these grasslands, and one old stallion has developed a way to stay one step ahead of his rivals. We follow Dorje as he shadows a herd of females and foals, from winter to summer, when he will get his chance to sire the next generation. But to win his prize he must eventually do battle with other stallions - all wanting his crown!

programme.title: Wildlife Icons 2 Ep6
programme.desc: Crocs and Hippos of Ndumo - The Nile crocodile and hippopotamus are two of Africas amphibious freshwater icons, found in waterways, rivers and lakes across the continent, including the stunning wilderness of Kwa-Zulu Natal in South Africa. These two species have co-existed for thousands of years, evolving in different ways to a life aquatic.

programme.title: Orangutan Jungle School 1 Ep2
programme.desc: Movin on Up - Best buds Valentino, Madara and Utris are ready for the next stage of forest school. Baby Clarita is at long last reunited with her mother. And toddler Mema discovers a tasty treat inside a rotten log (it can happen!).

programme.title: Kingdom of the Tide
programme.desc: Kingdom of the Tide - Low tide exposes a band of shore called the intertidal zone. Its a place of stunning extremes, attacked by hurricane force waves and exposed to baking heat. Creatures here have evolved in countless bizarre ways. Scientists explore this alien realm.
